                <note rend="inline" type="source">756.94/83a: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Japan</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Grew</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1940-05-11T14:00:00-04:00"
                            >May 11, 1940—2 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>148. The Department is releasing to the press a statement as follows:</p>
                <p>[Here follows text printed in <ref target="frus1931-41v02#pg_285">
                        <hi rend="italic">Foreign Relations</hi>, Japan, 1931–1941, volume II, page
                        285</ref>.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
